{
  "stem": "443.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But, meanwhile, we saw that the older people that they were already in the camp, they used to come around with those wagons, no horses.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "It was human-- human horses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Six people used to pull a wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And those people that couldn't walk, the elderly or disabled, they used to put them on those wagons, and they used take them away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going on, what's happening, where they take them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But then, after a while, we found out that they went into the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But we didn't know, the first couple days, we didn't know, really, what was going on, because we were selected to go to labor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "So I waited there a whole night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That day that we arrived, they told us to undress and take a shower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And after the shower, they gave us suits that looked like pajamas, pajamas that I have today, that's the pajamas.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That was the suit that we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Then after this was done, we-- we were told to stay in the line.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were giving us numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Everybody was-- whoever was going to that particular camp to that time, people used to get numbers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I have a number on my hand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "83146.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not sure, I have to look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you see what it say?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is it that--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "46?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that a 4?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you see through the camera?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Today, you would say, for sure, three months later, you're going to have AIDS, because they used the long needles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And every stop that you see, every spot that you see, was a long needle going down, all the way down to the bones.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next few days, my arm was so swollen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't even know what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
